273
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:13,900
Tonight.

274
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:35,500
Hi.

275
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,300
I bought some food.

276
00:13:41,300 --> 00:13:43,900
Let me help you with that.

277
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:45,400
Thank you.

278
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:48,400
My joints
are a little stiff.

279
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:51,300
Kevin,

280
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:54,700
why did you put your hood up
when i came in?

281
