339
00:17:13,300 --> 00:17:15,400
You should
bring your jacket.

340
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:23,700
She didn't say anything
on the way over?

341
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:25,500
Of course not,
kevin.

342
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:28,700
She hardly ever does.

343
00:17:30,700 --> 00:17:33,200
You're so brave.

344
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:36,700
I always wanted to
give it to you first.

345
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:39,700
I thought
you deserved an ability.

346
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:42,100
I'm sorry
it has to happen

347
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:44,900
