your permission.

348
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,200
Can i get this
started?

349
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:56,300
Give dr. Burkhoff your hand.

350
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:02,000
mommy
be late for school

