to make coffee.

391
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:25,100
Didn't tess like to draw?

392
00:19:37,800 --> 00:19:39,300
I feel like i'm in
a staring contest.

393
00:19:39,300 --> 00:19:41,700
It's okay.

394
00:19:41,700 --> 00:19:43,300
I know it can be
a little awkward

395
00:19:43,300 --> 00:19:44,700
at first.

396
00:19:44,700 --> 00:19:47,800
So, sometimes
when i'm having trouble

397
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:50,000
getting started
with a student,

398
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,400
i'll take their hand.

399
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:54,500
It helps everything
get rolling.

400
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:56,200
You up for it?

401
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,500
Yeah.

402
00:19:57,500 --> 00:19:59,300
I guess.

403
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:11,700
Just relax, okay?

404
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:13,600
Mm.

405
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:25,100
Oh.

406
00:20:25,100 --> 00:20:27,400
I'm sorry.
I, uh...

407
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:31,700
to be honest,
i felt a little awkward.

408
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:35,100
I, uh, i haven't
had someone touch me like that

409
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:38,100
since, uh...

410
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:41,000
my wife passed, and...

411
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:44,100
it's okay.

412
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,900
Sometimes
it takes more than one session

413
00:20:45,900 --> 00:20:47,100
to make headway.

414
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:54,300
[Distorted voice]:
Diana?

415
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,600
[Distorted]: Diana?

416
00:20:56,900 --> 00:20:57,800
[Normal voice]:
Should i just

