418
00:20:58,600 --> 00:20:59,300
I can handle this

419
00:20:59,300 --> 00:20:59,900
if you want.

420
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:01,200
No, i'm okay.

421
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,900
Any sign of tess?

422
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:04,400
No, she hasn't come out yet.

423
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,400
Look, tom.

424
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:06,400
I made an appointment
with the doctor

425
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,600
for tomorrow morning,

426
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:10,600
but, for now, i'd just like to
stick with it, okay?

427
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:16,200
I have to say,
this does not feel like the flu.

428
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,800
It's like
i'm dragging myself around.

429
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,700
Here she is.

430
00:21:28,700 --> 00:21:30,600
Come in.

431
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:32,900
Hey.

432
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:34,600
What?

433
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:37,500
Different look
for you.

434
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:39,500
"Look?"

435
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:42,100
I dressed like this
for 10 years.

436
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:45,000
Hey, you're not going to ask
about the wedding, are you?

437
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,700
I am officially
taking the night off

438
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:48,300
from all planning.

439
00:21:48,300 --> 00:21:50,900
This has nothing to do
with the wedding...

440
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:53,300
unless nick crowley's invited.

441
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:55,000
He's downstairs.

442
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,400
Really?

443
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,800
No, i'm getting ready
for his show.

444
00:21:57,800 --> 00:21:59,900
Maybe he wants to give me
a ride or something.

445
00:21:59,900 --> 00:22:02,000
Uh, i don't think
that's it.

446
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:04,700
Well, what?

447
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:08,100
[Slurring]:
I never get enough refills.

448
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:11,500
I mean, look at me...

449
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,800
What's he saying?

450
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:18,300
Nick has a prescription
for antabuse.

451
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:19,900
They're these pills

452
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:23,300
