i'm not taking no for an answer.

484
00:24:12,100 --> 00:24:13,100
Come on.

485
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:14,100
Actually,

486
00:24:14,100 --> 00:24:16,100
i think
you're going to have to.

487
00:24:17,300 --> 00:24:18,300
Diana?

488
00:24:18,300 --> 00:24:19,200
What the hell
are you doing?

489
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,200
I don't know, tom.

490
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,100
I'm sorry.

491
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:23,600
Diana's not quite
herself right now.

492
00:24:23,600 --> 00:24:25,300
She'll do
whatever tess wants her to.

493
00:24:25,300 --> 00:24:26,800
Tess,

494
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:28,300
will you get
his gun, please?

495
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:46,900
Please.

496
00:24:46,900 --> 00:24:48,800
