are you okay?

501
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,200
Are you all right?

502
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,900
I don't know.

503
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:06,800
What happened?

504
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:08,400
You pulled your gun
on me.

505
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:10,200
Tess?

506
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:12,000
Yeah.

507
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:12,900
