508
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:14,400
What?

509
00:25:14,400 --> 00:25:16,900
Something's wrong.

510
00:25:16,900 --> 00:25:19,300
I just feel weird.

511
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,600
Oh, my god.

512
00:25:20,600 --> 00:25:21,900
What are those?

513
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:23,600
They're lesions.

514
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:25,700
They're just like
the ones kevin had

515
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:28,800
when he started
taking promicin.

516
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:30,600
We need to get you
to ntac medical.

517
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:38,300
If there's anything at all
to these experiments

518
00:25:38,300 --> 00:25:39,800
dr. Burkhoff
has been conducting,

519
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:41,000
a lot of people in d.c.

520
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,300
Are going to want to
look over his notes.

521
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:43,400
These pictures
have already been circulated

522
00:25:43,400 --> 00:25:44,900
